8776.name: Fertilizer Price Index (2010 = 100) (World Bank (2017))
8776.description: The fertiliser price index, measured relative to real prices in 2010 (where 2010=100).

source.name: Fertilizer prices - World Bank (2017)
source.additionalInfo:
Fertilizer prices are measured as a real price index, where prices in 2010 are equal to 100 (2010 = 100).

Urea prices are reported in real US$ per metric ton.
